            <h1 className="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 tracking-tight">ATS-ChatBot <span className="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-lg mr-1 border border-indigo-100">v.0.1</span></h1>
            <p className="text-[10px] text-green-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 mt-0.5">
              <span className="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span> مساعدك الذكي الموثق
            </p>
